[South Africa has other existing foot-and-mouth disease (FMD) events. According to information reported to the OIE between January and April 2021, the situation for these events is as follows:

- Mpumalanga (OIE event ID 33576), FMD SAT 2, event status resolved (https://wahis.oie.int/#/report-info?reportId=16855)

- Limpopo (OIE event ID 36933), FMD SAT 1, event status ongoing (https://wahis.oie.int/#/report-info?reportId=32080)

- Limpopo (OIE event ID 28323), serotype not typed, event status ongoing (https://wahis.oie.int/#/report-info?reportId=30999)

- Limpopo (OIE event ID 32311), SAT 2, event status ongoing (https://wahis.oie.int/#/report-info?reportId=31000). - Mod.CRD

